<li>working with the filesystem</li>
<li>handling extensions and plugins</li>
<li>parsing static files</li>
<li>sending network requests</li>
</ul>
<p>Really few do CPU intensive tasks, like encoding and decoding some information.</p>
<p>You might be wondering what you have to do to benefit of this. It's easy! Just
