<p>The plugin can be found by searching for “Mozilla Persona” from the “Add New Plugin” page in the WordPress administration panel. Alternatively, it can be downloaded and manually installed from the <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/plugins/browserid/\" target=\"_blank\">Mozilla Persona</a> plugin page. Code is available on <a href=\"https://github.com/shane-tomlinson/browserid-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\">GitHub.</a></p>
