<p>Earlier this summer I had an amazing experience at <a href=\"https://adainitiative.org/what-we-do/events/\">AdaCamp </a> in San Francisco. The Melbourne and DC AdaCamps bore fruit too, as they connected so many women in open tech and culture with the communities I’m already part of, and made us visible to each other. </p>
