<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">In 2011 this wasn’t a thing. No one cared about it.</p>
<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Nearly a year later we were discussing specific policies on what we’d stream (public? internal?). A year later it was assumed everything we did would be streamed.</p>
<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Air Mozilla became one of the primary communication tools at Mozilla.</p>
