"font-size: x-small;\">mcoates </span><br /><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">mozillian</span>" nil nil "68e064976418e5452c2c8789c4825def") (386 (20968 62348 412502) "http://www.gavinsharp.com/blog/2013/07/18/changes-to-the-list-of-firefox-reviewers/" "Gavin Sharp: changes to the list of Firefox reviewers" "gavin" "Thu, 18 Jul 2013 22:26:58 +0000" "<p>I’ve made a few updates to the list of <a href=\"https://wiki.mozilla.org/Modules/Firefox\" title=\"Firefox reviewers\">Firefox reviewers</a>:</p>
