<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/taboca\">Marcio Galli</a> on exploring B2G/Gaia internals</li>
<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/fmarier\">François Marier</a> – <a href=\"http://hemingway.softwarelivre.org/fisl14/high/41a/sala41a-high-201307051001.ogg\">Persona</a>, or: User logins – can we do better than passwords and avoid centralized services? <em>(in English, slides in Portuguese)</em></li>
