</ul>
<p>(p.s.: if you want to see an entertaining explanation of how Persona works I highly recommend you watch François’ presentation at the 11’30″ mark)</p>
<p>The hackaton ran during the conference and finished on Saturday afternoon. We got a total of 7 apps submissions, which are all <a href=\"https://github.com/MozillaHackathon/fisl14\">posted on github</a>, and the winner was announced at the end of Surman’s talk and received a Geeksphone Keon! There were also e-books as prizes for other teams. Big props to Adriano, André Garzia and Morvana for running the hackaton!</p>
