<p>Some of this information was collected from other websites so it is only fair that I give credit where credit is due:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href=\"http://blog.margaretleibovic.com/post/36893756730/bugzilla-101\">Margaret Leibovic's Bugzilla 101</a></li>
<li><a href=\"http://blog.johnath.com/2010/02/04/bugzilla-for-humans/\">Johnath's Bugzilla for Humans</a></li>
