<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"thickbox no_icon\" href=\"http://cdn.benjaminkerensa.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/9136304328_a3a73bbd2f_c.jpg\" title=\"9136304328 a3a73bbd2f c 300x198 Firefox OS at Open Source Bridge\"><img alt=\"9136304328 a3a73bbd2f c 300x198 Firefox OS at Open Source Bridge\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-1949 aligncenter\" height=\"198\" src=\"http://cdn.benjaminkerensa.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/9136304328_a3a73bbd2f_c-300x198.jpg\" title=\"Firefox OS at Open Source Bridge\" width=\"300\" /></a></p>
