<p>including a couple that are now no longer around (<a href=\"https://drumbeat.org\">mozilla drubmeat</a>) and the ‘old’ (or better sounding version 1.0) of <a href=\"https://webmaker.org\">webmaker.org</a>. I also contributed code to <a href=\"https://mozillalabs.com/projects/\">Mozilla Labs</a>, <a href=\"https://mozilla.org\">mozilla.org</a> and even removed a <blink> from <a href=\"http://myfavoritebeer.org/\">the very first demo-site showing Mozilla Persona</a>!</p>
