<pre class=\"literal-block\">65 files changed, 6164 insertions(+), 2716 deletions(-)
</pre>
<p>That's a lot of change for a small project like this.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p>If you're using ElasticUtils, I highly encourage you to update to
