<a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://support.mozilla.org/\">Support</a> already.</p>
<p>For the complete list of what's new, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://elasticutils.readthedocs.org/en/v0.7/changelog.html#version-0-7-released-june-12th-2013\">What's new in Version 0.7</a>.</p>
<p>Many thanks to everyone who helped out: Erik Rose, Jannis Leidel, Rob
Hudson, Steve Ivy, Will Kahn-Greene (oh, that's me!), Chris McDonald,
Ricky Rosario, James Socol, Giorgos Logiotatidis, Mike Cooper,
Grégoire Vigneron, Chris Sinchok and Brandon Adams.</p>
<p>If you have any questions, let us know! We hang out on <tt class=\"docutils literal\">#elasticutils</tt>
on irc.mozilla.org.</p>
</div>
<p>
